  "subject": "feat(projects): add project detail pages with mirrored docs from all repos",
  "body": "Each project now has a detail page (project.html?name=...) with:\n- Metadata: audience, use cases, data/privacy, tech stack, status\n- Tabbed doc viewer: Overview, User Guide, Testing Guide, Tutorial\n- Copy markdown and raw file buttons per doc\n- Custom markdown renderer (no external dependencies)\n\nFetched and mirrored docs from all 10 active repos. Private repo\ndocs (graphiki, few-lap, synctone, tool-till-tees) scrubbed to\nremove env vars, database strings, local URLs, and infrastructure\ndetails. Tutorial content extracted from TutorialModal components\ninto standalone TUTORIAL.md files for 5 projects.\n\nAdded reference docs: PROJECT_DOCS_STATUS.md tracks doc coverage\nand outstanding work. DOCS_UPDATE_GUIDE.md documents the process\nfor fetching, scrubbing, and updating mirrored docs in future.\n\nTags: projects, docs, portfolio, privacy, multi-page\nComplexity: 4\nUrgency: 2\nImpact: user-facing\nRisk: low\nDebt: neutral\nEpic: portfolio-site\nSemver: minor\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01Bh93JoHZAKz7zY48tGvfZ1",
